== 获奖项 ==
{{main|《点球成金》获奖名单}}《点球成金》在[[第84屆奧斯卡金像獎|第84屆奧斯卡金像獎]]角逐获[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]、[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|男主角]]、[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|男配角]]、[[奧斯卡最佳改編劇本獎|原著改编]]等六项提名，但均未胜出<ref name="Oscars">{{cite web|title=The 84th Academy Awards (2012) Nominees and Winners|url=https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2012|access-date=2021-05-15|date=2012-02-26|publisher=[[电影艺术与科学学院|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505084644/https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2012|archive-date=2021-05-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片在[[第69屆金球獎|第69屆金球獎]]入围四项，[[第65届英国电影学院奖|第65届英国电影学院奖]]入围三项，[[第16届卫星奖|第16届卫星奖]]入围四项，并拿下[[2011年纽约影评人协会奖|2011年纽约影评人协会奖]][[纽约影评人协会奖最佳男主角|最佳男主角]]和[[纽约影评人协会奖最佳剧本|剧本]]两项大奖。彼特与希爾均获[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]提名，[[2011年美國電影學會獎|美国影艺协会]]、[[2011年达拉斯—沃斯堡影评人协会奖|达拉斯—沃斯堡影评人协会奖]]均把本片列入2011年十大佳片。[[非裔美国人影评人协会|非裔美国人影评人协会]]把本片排在年度第六，[[凯瑞斯·多西|凯瑞斯·多西]]演绎版歌曲《[[蘭卡的異想世界_(歌曲)|蘭卡的異想世界]]》获最佳歌曲奖<ref name="AAFCAWins">{{cite news|archive-date=2020-11-28|url=https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2011/12/african-american-critics-tree-of-life-best-film-2011.html|title=African American critics name 'The Tree of Life' best film of 2011|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|last=Kaufman|first=Amy|date=2011-12-12|access-date=2021-05-15|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128172331/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2011/12/african-american-critics-tree-of-life-best-film-2011.html}}</ref>{{refn|《[[蘭卡的異想世界_(歌曲)|蘭卡的異想世界]]》是澳大利亚流行歌手[[蘭卡|蘭卡]]2008年录制的歌曲<ref>{{cite news | archive-date = 2018-06-12 | dead-url = no | first = Andrew | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612135814/https://www.seattletimes.com/entertainment/music/moneyball-and-the-myth-of-the-wise-kid/ | url = https://www.seattletimes.com/entertainment/music/moneyball-and-the-myth-of-the-wise-kid/ | title = 'Moneyball' and the myth of the wise kid | work = [[西雅图时报|The Seattle Times]] | last = Matson | date = 2011-10-31 | access-date = 2021-05-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=dQmSBAAAQBAJ&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | title = Deconstructing Brad Pitt | publisher = Bloomsbury Publishing | location = [[纽约|New York City]] | last1 = Schaberg | first1 = Chirstopher | last2 = Bennett | first2 = Robert | date = 2014-10-09 | isbn = 978-1-62356-396-7 | pages = 31, 35 | access-date = 2021-05-18 | archive-date = 2021-05-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210514170459/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=dQmSBAAAQBAJ&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | dead-url = no }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。[[廣播音樂公司|廣播音樂公司]]向为本片作曲的[[麥可·唐納|麥可·唐納]]颁发[[广播音乐公司奖|最佳电影音乐奖]]，米勒获[[好萊塢電影獎|好萊塢電影獎]]最佳导演。2011年《[[乡村之声|乡村之声]]》杂志电影民调的最佳男主角和编剧项目本片均位居前十。

